            'Duplicate c√≥ th·ªÉ l√† m·ªôt v·∫•n ƒë·ªÅ l·ªõn khi ch√∫ng c√≥ th·ªÉ l√†m gi·∫£m hi·ªáu su·∫•t v√† l√£ng ph√≠ b·ªô nh·ªõ.\n<br>Sau ƒë√¢y l√† m·ªôt v√†i c√°ch ƒë·ªÉ lo·∫°i b·ªè ch√∫ng:\n# Lo·∫°i b·ªè duplicate s·ª≠ d·ª•ng t·ª´ kh√≥a DISTINCT\nM·ªôt trong nh·ªØng c√°ch ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n nh·∫•t l√† s·ª≠ d·ª•ng t·ª´ kh√≥a **DISTINCT**. B·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ s·ª≠ d·ª•ng n√≥ v·ªõi c√¢u l·ªánh **SELECT** ƒë·ªÉ nh·∫≠n v·ªÅ nh·ªØng gi√° tr·ªã duy nh·∫•t c·ªßa m·ªôt column.<br>\nC√∫ ph√°p:\n```SQL\nSELECT DISTINCT column_name\nFROM table_name\n```\n# Lo·∫°i b·ªè duplicate s·ª≠ d·ª•ng c√¢u l·ªánh GROUP BY\nM·ªôt c√°ch kh√°c ƒë·ªÉ lo·∫°i b·ªè duplicate l√† s·ª≠ d·ª•ng c√¢u l·ªánh **GROUP BY**. N√≥ ƒë∆∞·ª£c d√πng ƒë·ªÉ nh√≥m c√°c h√†ng c√≥ c√πng gi√° tr·ªã trong column, do ƒë√≥ n√≥ th∆∞·ªùng ƒëi v·ªõi c√°c h√†m t·ªïng h·ª£p nh∆∞ **COUNT(), SUM(), AVG(), MAX(), MIN()** ƒë·ªÉ t√≠nh to√°n cho t·ª´ng nh√≥m.<br>\n·ªû ƒë√¢y ta ch·ªâ d√πng **GROUP BY** cho m·ª•c ƒë√≠ch lo·∫°i b·ªè duplicate trong m·ªôt column n√™n c√∫ ph√°p s·∫Ω l√†:\n```SQL\nSELECT column_name\nFROM table_name\nGROUP BY column_name\n```\n# Lo·∫°i b·ªè duplicate s·ª≠ d·ª•ng c√¢u l·ªánh INNER JOIN\nC√¢u l·ªánh **INNER JOIN** th∆∞·ªùng d√πng ƒë·ªÉ combine c√°c h√†ng t·ª´ hai ho·∫∑c nhi·ªÅu b·∫£ng d·ª±a tr√™n column chung gi·ªØa ch√∫ng ƒë·ªÉ truy v·∫•n th√¥ng tin. B·∫±ng c√°ch s·ª≠ d·ª•ng **INNER JOIN** cho ch·ªâ m·ªôt b·∫£ng, ta c√≥ th·ªÉ lo·∫°i b·ªè duplicate.<br>\nC√∫ ph√°p:\n```SQL\nSELECT a.column_name\nFROM table_name a\nINNER JOIN table_name b ON a.column_name = b.column_name\nWHERE a.primary_key > b.primary_key\n```\nV√≠ d·ª• ta c√≥ b·∫£ng employees v·ªõi 3 c·ªôt "employee_id", "employee_name" v√† "department_id". Ta s·∫Ω lo·∫°i b·ªè duplicate trong c·ªôt department_id nh∆∞ sau:\n```SQL\nSELECT a.department_id\nFROM employees a\nINNER JOIN employees b ON a.department_id = b.department_id\nWHERE a.employee_id > b.employee_id\n```\n# K·∫øt lu·∫≠n\nRemember to always make a backup of your data before modifying it to avoid any potential data loss.\n\n\n-----\nSource: https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-remove-duplicate-data-in-sql/',
